// ARGN3 --> race (1=human, 2=elf, 3=gargoyle)
// ARGS  --> account name
// ARGO  --> the client creating the character
// RETURN
//	  0 --> normal action (create character)
//	  1 --> denyes creation

IF (<ARGN3>==2)	//Uncomment this code to disable the racial bonus of MaxMana +20 for Elfs
 MaxMana
ENDIF

IF <ARGN3> != 1
  RETURN 1
ENDIF

